{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125308, "create_time": 1652933970, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "不应该，为了保护我们一半的人民。实在想要代孕到国外代去，不要霍霍本国的妹子。\n不过即使在国外，代孕合法的地区也是少数了。", "timestamp": 1652933970}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125311, "create_time": 1652934022, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "#44106", "timestamp": 1652934022}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125314, "create_time": 1652934130, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 美国的一些州，俄罗斯乌克兰这些，还有法国和一些小国", "timestamp": 1652934130}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125315, "create_time": 1652934157, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 被举报了，可以说一下内容吗", "timestamp": 1652934157}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125330, "create_time": 1652934758, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "应该放开代孕，给生育权一个合理的市场定价！", "timestamp": 1652934758}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125335, "create_time": 1652935007, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "不提伦理，放开的话，一方面，家里经济条件比较差的姑娘就很可能迫于家里人压力出来代孕，很难谈得上自愿，另一方面不知道会不会导致一些犯罪，把人拐去生孩子…不过cz也比较困惑，合法化究竟是会鼓励这种产业，还是能规范化原来已有的地下产业。确保从业者都是自愿的并非容易的事情。", "timestamp": 1652935007}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125347, "create_time": 1652935178, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "不应该，代孕存在的原因是有收入不高的女性为了收入才进行的，因为对于行动和其他方面的影响，绝大多数有钱的女性不会去从事这一行业，理论上这种行为代表了资产阶级对于无产阶级女性身体上的进一步剥削，所以在中国理论上不可能开放代孕合法化", "timestamp": 1652935178}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125356, "create_time": 1652935341, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Eve: 话是这样说，假如开放代孕能提高生育率我真的怀疑政府会不会这么做", "timestamp": 1652935341}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125359, "create_time": 1652935357, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Dave: 不可能规范化原有的产业的…这么多人还自愿加班996呢…也没见规范化。\n提高打击力度，见到在本土组织代孕的直接取缔判刑，这才能真正保护到人。", "timestamp": 1652935357}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125362, "create_time": 1652935443, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Francis: 但是可以开放海外代孕呀，别人国家的人民，他们国家政府自己不保护，我们也鞭长莫及保护不着。如果有方便的渠道海外代孕，或许也可以提高生育率，而且不祸害我们自己的人民。", "timestamp": 1652935443}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125371, "create_time": 1652935598, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "支持代孕，给蝈蝻做免费生育机器有什么好的，不如光明正大出来卖。", "timestamp": 1652935598}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125372, "create_time": 1652935622, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Alice: 什么叫祸害，你不想做就不做呗，干预别人自由选择才是祸害", "timestamp": 1652935622}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125399, "create_time": 1652936049, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Grace: 说过了，这里面没有自由选择。你都不能自由的选择不自愿加班，凭什么假定别人就能自由的选择不自愿代孕？\n按照你的逻辑，卖肾也可以放开，你为什么干涉别人卖血卖肾的自由呢？再说你们男拳师意见最大的不就是彩礼，你没钱给彩礼可以去卖肾赚钱啊，这不是你的自由吗？", "timestamp": 1652936049}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 125417, "create_time": 1652936451, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "这和我党理念方针不符，不太可能开放...", "timestamp": 1652936451}], "create_time": 1652933500, "cw": null, "hot_score